            "testimonial": {},
            "productTabs": [
                {
                    "layout": "two-column",
                    "title": "Overview",
                    "description": {
                        "html": "<div class=“ewa-rteLine“>Whether you're looking to manage weight, or you just want a convenient option for everyday health, Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix is the solution to give your body what it needs without sacrificing taste or convenience.</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>&nbsp;</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix is your go-to meal replacement shake for a healthier lifestyle. If you&rsquo;re looking for an easy-to-make, delicious, on-the-go option for weight management or everyday health, Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix has you covered.</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>&nbsp;</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>Enjoy this shake as a nutritious alternative for one or two of your main meals, or simply as a way to improve your current diet. Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix is formulated to ensure you're getting the right balance of nutrients while keeping your calorie count in check.</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>&nbsp;</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>It provides a balanced blend of essential nutrients, including proteins, carbohydrates, healthy fats, vitamins and minerals. It's a smart and effective way to support your weight management or wellness goals without compromising your health or energy levels.</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>&nbsp;</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix fits into your lifestyle exactly how you need it. With a variety of flavours, there is something to satisfy everyone's taste.</div>"
                    },
                    "descriptionLeft": {},
                    "descriptionRight": {},
                    "accordion": [],
                    "image": {
                        "altText": "Woman drinking Formula 1 shake at home",
                        "ariaLabel": "Woman drinking Formula 1 shake at home",
                        "desktopImage": {
