                {
                    "layout": "single-column",
                    "title": "Features and Benefits",
                    "description": {
                        "html": "<div class=“ewa-rteLine“><div class=“ewa-rteLine“><ul><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Provides 9 g of high-quality protein* per serving</li><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Provides 3 g of dietary fibre per serving</li><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Contains 18 vitamins and minerals</li><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Has approx. 94.2 Kcal (powder only) per serving</li><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Is a Low Glycaemic Index food**</li><li class=“ewa-rteLine“>Contains 30 servings</li></ul><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>Please refer to product label for detailed information.</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“>&nbsp;</div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“><em>*Protein Digestibility Corrected Amino Acid Score (PDCAAS) of 1</em></div><div class=“ewa-rteLine“><em>**Formula 1 Nutritional shake mix is tested for GI. The testing was conducted according to the Internationally recognized methodology (ISO 26642).</em></div>"
                    },
