                        "thumbnailAltText": "Herbalife Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix Mango 750g Nutritional Information",
                        "thumbnailAriaLabelText": "Herbalife Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix Mango 750g Nutritional Information"
                    },
                    "ingredients": {
                        "html": "<p>Soy Protein Isolate, Fructose Powder, Lecithin Powder, Whey Protein Concentrate, Oat Fiber, Artificial mango flavouring substance, Stabilizer (Guar gum - INS 412), Inulin, Bulking Agent [Cellulose Powder - INS 460 (ii)], Soybean Oil Powder, Corn Powder, Calcium Caseinate, Potassium Chloride, Turmeric Rhizome Extract Powder, Minerals ,Diluent [Dicalcium Phosphate - INS 341 (ii)], Vitamins, Sodium Caseinate, Psyllium Husk Powder, Zingiber officinale Rhizome Powder, Emulsifier (Glyceryl monostearate - INS 471), Sweetener (Sucralose - INS 955), Stabilizer [Dipotassium hydrogen phosphate -INS 340 (ii)], Papain Powder, Antioxidant (Ascorbyl palmitate - INS 304).<br /> <br /> This contains Sucralose. CONTAINS NON-CALORIC SWEETENER.</p>"
                    },
                    "allergenInfo": {
                        "html": "CONTAINS MILK, SOY & OATS."
                    },
                    "productTabIndex": "pTabIngredients"
                },
                {
                    "layout": "single-column",
                    "title": "How to use",
                    "description": {
                        "html": "<p>INSTRUCTION OF USE:</p><p>Gently shake the canister prior to each use as contents may settle.</p><p>For meal replacement - Simply blend, shake or stir 25 g (3 scoops) of Formula 1 with 300 ml of skimmed milk OR 25 g (3 scoops) of Formula 1 with 2 scoops of Shakemate with 300 ml water and enjoy.</p><p>Not to exceed the recommended daily usage.</p><p>RECOMMENDED USAGE LEVEL:</p><p>For Weight Control: Replace two meals daily with a Formula 1 shake and eat one nutritious meal to support weight loss.</p><p>For Weight Management: Replace one meal daily with a Formula 1 shake to maintain/manage your weight.</p><p>Target consumer group : Adults</p><p>This product is not for parenteral use. The product is not to be used by pregnant, nursing, and lactating women or children under 5 years, adolescents and elderly, except when medically advised by physician or certified dietician or nutrition professional. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. Herbalife products are designed for use by adults as a part of a healthy well-balanced diet. Our products are formulated for adults and are labelled based on the adult Recommended Dietary Allowances. Before using this product as part of a weight control/ management program it is also advisable to consult a physician. Herbalife does not recommend (except under the supervision of a physician) that children/adolescents consume Herbalife products for weight loss, especially during their formative years.</p><p>Store with lid tightly closed in a cool, dry place, away from sunlight. Recommended to consume the product within 30 days once the canister is opened. Product is required to be stored out of reach of children.</p>"
                    },
